channel.title: Project Fnatic- Professional remake of the golden days ~~ thread updated
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq20/nathanz1_2008/banner.png[/img]
[B][FONT=Franklin Gothic Medium]Welcome to project fnatic! This is a professional remake of the classic game "runescape" in 2006 i started a couple of months ago. We will be appointing every detail of the game to make it inch perfect for our players. We can offer our maturity and professionalism in both our staff and community.
Unlike the other remakes which have been riddled with bugs and backstabbing staff.
We make a promise to update everyday, and help and treat every single player the same.
We would like to involve our players even though the BETA won't be released for a few weeks, every weekend we plan on opening the server in hope that the players can make it even faster for us to release this! What we ask is that the community logs in and reports any bugs or missing content which would save us uncountable hours so we can concentrate on the more important aspects. Updates will happen everyday, whether the server is on or off, we refuse to give up and strive to achieve the #1 remake spot no matter the critisicm.[/FONT][/B] [B][U]Please join our forum[/U][/B]: [url=http://www.project-fnatic.net]Project Fnatic- Professional remake- No Fuss[/url]
[size=18pt]Also we are looking for a professional staff team for community management or development, apply on forums.[/size]
Here's some of the features:
[B][U]Combat:[/U][/B] [color=green]*PvP fully complete *Perfect max hit formulas *Perfect accuracy formula *Equipment requirements[/COLOR]
[B][U]Magic:[/U][/B] [color=green]*Every modern combat spell *Can't mage through walls *Staves that give unlimited amount of runes working *Bones to bananas *Bones to Peache's *Weakening spells *bind, snare, entangle *Teleports, teleothers *Alching *Superheat *Enchanting jewelry[/COLOR]
[B][U]Prayer:[/U][/B] [color=green]*All bones bury-able *Every prayer working properly *Prayer bonus affects prayer drain rate[/COLOR]
Mining: [color=green]*Emptying and refilling rocks *All ores can be mined *Correct pickaxe finding and animations *Prospecting *Random chance of obtaining gems *Correct depleting of rocks chance algorithms[/COLOR]
Firemaking: [color=green]*All logs light able *Adding and depleting of lightened logs *Ashes appear after logs burn out *Correct animations *Clipped[/COLOR]
[B][U]Woodcutting[/U][/B] [color=green]*Stumps and regrowing trees *Correct hatchet finding *Correct hatchet animations[/COLOR]
Crafting: 100% *Cutting gems *Making amulets, necklaces, and rings *Stringing amulets *Tanning normal and hard leather *Crafting normal and hard leather.. *Spinning wool *Making pottery
[B][U]Cooking:[/U][/B] *All fish can be cooked *All meats can be cooked *Grinding wheat into flour *Cakes *Pies *Pizza *Stew *Wine *Correct burning formula *Lumbridge cooking range bonus *Eating food (in pieces) *Correct animation and timing used
[B][U]Rune crafting 100%:[/U][/B] [color=green]*Multiple rune crafting *All alters *Pouches *Talisman Locating[/COLOR]
[B][U]Quests:[/U][/B] Cook's Assistant[/COLOR] Others in progress.
[u][b]*Vbulletin Forums[/b][/u]
The server now has thousands of npcs, every city is mapped out perfectly with 95% of all the dialogues in runescape.
It is perfected in every way. Every skill is working and every miscanious including random events and clue scrolls.
Come join the no.1 remake. No fuss.
A video of combat: [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_QrZ4ooBHU&feature=youtu.be[/youtube]
